<!-- ID 11 is the resource library white paper download page -->
<!-- if set to false so page will display -->
												<h2 class="title">Membership Application Process</h2>
<p>Applying for membership is easy. Just follow these simple steps and you are on your way to becoming a part of one of the most dynamic industry organizations in the world.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/downloads/Alliance ByLaws">Review the ByLaws</a> for IPSO Alliance membership and the annual dues requirements before submitting your application.</li>
<li>Complete the <a href="/downloads/Membership Agreement">application form</a> to apply for membership. Once your application is received, you will receive notification of the results within 5 business days. If your application is approved an invoice for your dues payment will be sent. Payment may be made by check to [IPSO Alliance] or via EFT (electronic funds transfer).</li>
<li>If you have questions, please contact us by email at<br />
<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">
// Copyright © 2005 Voormedia - WWW.VOORMEDIA.COM
